Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of the 400s and 500s and up is actually quantum mechanics and of course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.35,0:01:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the Heisenberg principle explains why healings work, why prayer works. It gives
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.00,0:01:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,some kind of a scientific respectability and this is a, we talked about Henry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.28,0:01:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stapp's website, is a good place to pick it up where the Schrodinger earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.37,0:01:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,condition is activated by the Heisenberg principle and collapses the wave
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.15,0:01:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,function, which is the way we can say in quantum mechanics what we say in just
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.04,0:01:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual teaching, that potentiality becomes actuality when conditions are
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.87,0:01:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,appropriate and one of the conditions that is appropriate in the proximate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.95,0:01:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,field is intention. So I like Wayne Dyer's book he picked up on intention to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.26,0:01:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,demonstrate its importance by showing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.43,0:01:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,what's your intention and we tend to manifest, we tend to manifest things due
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to intention because the potentiality actualizes as the collapse of the wave
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:02:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,function. Okay next, so that just proves you can be spiritual and also scientific
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,right. I know more about Heisenberg quantum mechanics than a lot of physicists do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.24,0:02:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because it's like a reflection of the spiritual reality which is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,already second nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, in which you see emergence, emergence. You don't see causality, you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,say potential. So the world is, what you're seeing is the emergence of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,potentiality continuously. It's not cause and effect, there's not a this and a that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The this is emerging into actuality in the three-dimensional expression because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,on the level of consciousness it exists already as potentiality. Yeah, Sheldrake
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.99,0:02:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of course, Sheldrake's principle and I think it was very important. Not, not too
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.09,0:02:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,many people quote, more people should quote Sheldrake than they do I think in
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the world of physics because I thought it was a very important phenomenon. Okay so the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Newtonian paradigm as you see, things are forced, caused, provable, measurable. This
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is the world of the ego, it is also the world of science. And then quantum
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,mechanics we're moving on to a whole different viewpoint of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We see non-local coherence, we see potential, we see the time-dependent and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,independent phenomena, and the whole world of stochastic or so-called
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,chaotic. And in our work those are attractor fields. So on the scale of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness each one of those levels represents an attractor field from the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,viewpoint of nonlinear dynamics. It has an energy to it. Just as I say there's only
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.86,0:03:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,one orange cat in the whole universe. That's an attractor field of orange
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,cat-ness out of which emerges its representations as living orange, orange
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:04:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,kitties. But all of them are controlled by the same attractor field. Orange
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,kitties don't bark. In the attractor field of kittiness they mew. So anyway that creates a
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,certain amount of order. So in nonlinear dynamics these are called attractor fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them are very powerful. This is why I tell people do not fool around. Do
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,not fool around with deviant pathways just out of curiosity. Get your kicks
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,some other way. People go to what do they call those New Age fairs. People say
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,well I'm going to spend the weekend with New Age fair people here and doing this and that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course I'm not going to be affected by it because I don't
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.43,0:04:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,believe in it. That's amazing illusion. That's how you're lit over the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,when you come back from that, and I've done it with many people, you say well I went
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,there and there are very nice people I know all the time and I didn't believe
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:05:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,any of it. They weren't affected by it. Except why do I have to clear myself up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,after I just got through talking to them? Because they picked up so much weird
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,negative energy vibrations in their aura. Their aura is full of crap they picked
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,up from all these people because these people are wanderers through the New Age
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.86,0:05:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,forest and they're full of it. If you looked at their aura with a spectroscope you'd say, oh, oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. God almighty. You'd wear a mask, you know what I mean? You'd
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,put on gloves when you shake hands with them. Sterilizer when you do because
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you pick up all kinds of energies that are looking for your chinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you think you're beyond chinkism? No. I'll tell you why. What did the Buddha say at the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,very end? He says, I was beset by demons. You're talking about the Buddha, you're not talking about Sedona spiritual aspirin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:06:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha was beset by demons and you think you're not going to be, you're going to walk
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,through the muck field and then come and visit me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well because of sophistication and many years experience I know this phenomena and I'm aware
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,of what it is, I usually intuit what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There are usually appeals to vanity and various things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.66,0:06:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway so you know what to clear in yourself, you know what to clear in yourself, what to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,pray for, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But the average person thinks that they have not been affected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to smudge the house after they visit you and they think they have been unaffected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's those negative spirits and demons running all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're not going to walk through the field and that come out with stickers on you, ain't
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Buddha had that complaint, what's your chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to go out and hang out with people that are surrounded by demons, is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All kinds of white magic and black magic and God knows what.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Tarot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Alistair Crowley, The Golden Dawn, do you think you can read Alistair Crowley, play
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.45,0:07:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the Tarot deck, the Crowley deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.85,0:07:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask what's the Crowley deck at.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The Crowley deck tolerates over 60, 55.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.07,0:07:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to play with the Crowley deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me you had a good time at the New Age Fair, had your cards read, and it didn't affect
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it affected you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the guides on the other side do so well, because your weakness is transparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Transparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like a germ knows where to feed on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're transparent to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,These spirit guides on the other side, Master Poo Poo and Palaba and Gaba, they all know
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a fancy name, intuit from the psychic realm what you're thinking has got you the minute
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you sit down for a reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.76,0:08:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They've already got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They just read you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They just read you, got you just where you want to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So of course they sound impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They sound impressive because anybody who's psychic can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had psychic friends over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had psychic friends over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is intuitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.66,0:08:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan is very psychic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm holding something in mind, she'll say, oh, so and so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.86,0:09:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Not through mental processing, not through linear cognitive functioning, just knows it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You get the energy field, and the energy field tells you what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's called women's intuition, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Men have it in business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,See, women have it, but men have it also in business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I just get this deal, I'm going to work with this SOB.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.48,0:09:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, he's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Men don't accept it as intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They think that that's a womanly thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman respects it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She respects it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And look at all the troubles she's saving herself, reading all those dopey books.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to read the great books of the Western world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say something to her and she'll say, that's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me check it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Instant knowingness, instant knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So we value intuition then, it's really a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But I believe, you know, my male brain says, yeah, but check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:10:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So she says, this is what it is, and then I say, okay, well check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So now you've got both the masculine and the feminine view of how to check out reality
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,through intuitive knowingness, and then the male brain says, yeah, but let's check it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,out through the intellect, let's calibrate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What did we just calibrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.77,0:10:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, the card, I wasn't going to bring it up, but it just came up, so I guess God
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted me to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.13,0:10:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So I say, don't fool around with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to spend a number of lifetimes wandering around the esoteric world, I'm not
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,saying you shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And certainly all of us, when we got involved in it, had a curiosity, see the child's curiosity?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what they play on, the child's curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.59,0:10:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a reading, please do the cards, let's do a psychic, let's go into a trance, let's
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.02,0:10:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,throw the runes, let's throw the stones, let's throw the marbles, let's throw the dice, let's
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,throw the ... Look at the attraction of that, the attraction of it, to the child's curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you can leave your curious child at home and go to a New Age fair, fine, but if
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it wasn't for your curious child, you wouldn't even be there, so you can't leave them home,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's who went to the fair in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She makes threatening gestures when it's time to break.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so we'll take a break and then we'll resume at what time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We resume at two o'clock, and thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:12:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll resume when we're left off, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,God, I didn't know there were so many people here all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to resume.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to resume now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of this is familiar territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,As I say, according to the Colin Ock principle, the more often you hear it, the more it becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,your own natural way of being, just through familiarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So one way to learn things is through familiarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so familiar with it that imagine getting in a cockpit of one of these planes and reading
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be old and gray before you finish the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you've got to be able to do it, and I do a lot of things spatially.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know where they are, but I know by reaching this way, I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's just my orientation of life is spatial.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When I put a tool away, I know where it is, and the next time I'm in a tool room, I just
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,reach there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't look at it, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is sort of handy, I guess, for what I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But everybody has a different way of processing information.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people are mainly auditory, some people are linear, you know, visual.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just noticed that I, when we were talking about it, that I'm very spatial.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I reach for this because I know where it is, but I don't remember where it is at
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's just familiarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the easiest way to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I had to go through school again, I'd just do the Colin Ock principle, frankly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,save myself all that memorizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Newtonian paradigm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is in the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the world of logic and causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the world of science.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And the nearest thing to it is quantum mechanics, which is the next direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can go from Newtonian science into quantum mechanics and advanced theoretical
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,physics.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the next emergence is into a different paradigm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So the reason for the Scopes Trial, you see, because I'm writing about that now, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.94,0:14:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Scopes Trial is not resolvable, the Scopes Dilemma is not resolvable, because what you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,had was the presentation of two different paradigms, two different paradigms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.33,0:14:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So Clarence Durow was coming from the Newtonian scientific paradigm of the mid-400s, and Bryant
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,was coming from the 500s and up, which is a different paradigm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:15:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot argue the paradigm of the 400s against the 500s, or vice versa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.44,0:15:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So there was no meeting of minds, because they're two different paradigms.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So my resolution of the Scopes paradigm, confrontation between science and faith, is that you have
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,to have a paradigm that is large enough to be inclusive of both.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't have the either or or, you have so kind of, the calibrated level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is inclusive of all domains, it goes from 500 up to 500, so you've got something big
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.79,0:15:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can just see that they were in different positions within this overall context.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So there isn't really a conflict, they're just two different paradigms of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But you cannot resolve it, because you cannot resolve it, you cannot apply science to spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,reality, nor can you apply spiritual reality to science.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot resolve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no meeting of the minds there, they're two different paradigms.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:16:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So as I say, it's like, to try and do so is like looking for ghosts with a Geiger counter,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you just got the wrong instrument.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.35,0:16:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're all familiar with the Newtonian paradigm, of course, and the quantum mechanics begins
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to take us beyond that, up to the next paradigm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So it is sort of an area of transition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll move on from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And this has to do with getting rid of the dualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.66,0:16:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So that you see that heat is not the opposite of cold, and truth is, you know, falsehood
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is not the opposite of truth, it's the absence of truth, and cold is the absence of heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So the mind tends to create dualities where there are none, there's only gradations, so
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the calibrated levels of consciousness are the same, there's gradations, gradations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:17:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So we know that boiling is at 212 and freezing at 32.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, one to a thousand was arbitrary, and I always tell people you can make up your
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,own scale, you know, from one to a hundred, or from a hundred to ten thousand, or whatever
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you want, and then you will end up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll just move on to see that duality is an artifact of mentation, see, an artifact
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of mentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.26,0:17:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual practices, this I think is valuable, because it gives validity to many of the things
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,we do, and it gives recognition to the essence of things that we were not aware was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lord's Prayer, the sound, Om, and you see the difference between the sound Om and
