Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.63,0:19:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,have coins in their finger, in their hands, and they're going like this to the music,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to the sound of the flutes, and clinking the coins, as they go like this, it was like unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Transport you to a different realm, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pilgrimages to Mecca, yogic chants, AA is 540, it's probably, to me, the most successful
