Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:19:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It does not indulge in self-gratification or aggrandizement, it has no great buildings,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,it has no huge money.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No coercion, everyone's free to come and go, and it represents, to me, pure spirituality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So this was born of genius, and of course, Bill Wilson, if you calibrate, when he finally
