Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That was well up in the 500s, but out of that moment arose the salvation of millions worldwide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.81,0:21:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So that is the power, spiritual power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.81,0:21:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.81,0:21:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of that arose, then unfolded, what to me is probably the purest spiritual organization
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,in existence today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Extremely powerful, transformative.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.81,0:21:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And it set the paradigm of spiritual purity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It really set the paradigm of integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,At the Golden Rule at 405, you never hear the Golden Rule anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't hearing anybody quote the Golden Rule in 20, 30 years.
