Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.98,0:21:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The public is all full of rights, you know, these are my rights, these are my rights.
