Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.07,0:24:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The progressive fields of realization are very useful in meditation,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.07,0:24:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,because in meditation you keep letting go of this, you keep letting go of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.07,0:24:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you realize what's going on is that you're watching it,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.07,0:24:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and how do you know you're watching it out of awareness?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.07,0:25:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's relatively easy in meditation to let all this go
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.36,0:25:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and allow yourself to be the observer witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.36,0:25:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The observer witness is a very comfortable place to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.36,0:25:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can live in the observer witness all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.36,0:25:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and a contemplative person tends to.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.36,0:25:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the observer and the witness, but you have no reaction to it, no commitment to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.36,0:25:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If it disappears, it's okay. If it appears again, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.36,0:25:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have any stake in what's happening in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.36,0:25:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,because you see that all you're doing is witnessing the phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.36,0:25:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Witnessing the phenomena without personal involvement
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.36,0:25:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,or identification.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.36,0:25:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is a very good place to pull back to, the observer witness,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.36,0:25:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and from there it's quite easy for the awareness of the light of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.36,0:25:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to be aware that your consciousness is an independent field in and of itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.52,0:25:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and that what it's conscious of, or the content of it, is relatively irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.52,0:26:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because if it isn't this, then it's going to be that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.58,0:26:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the question about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.58,0:26:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If it isn't this, it's going to be that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.72,0:26:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So pulling yourself back and identifying here is not that difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.72,0:26:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That can be done just to know that this is possible already enables you to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.72,0:26:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And then one day, all of this disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.72,0:26:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no observer or witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.72,0:26:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only consciousness being conscious as awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.72,0:26:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And you realize neither there's not a witness or an observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.72,0:26:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only the awareness of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.72,0:26:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And as that disappears, then you realize the Self with a capital S.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.72,0:26:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay, next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.42,0:26:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.22,0:26:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Important to spiritual evolution and things the world doesn't realize
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.22,0:27:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is that spiritual evolution now triggers from consciousness level 200 up,
