Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.22,0:27:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,which gets stronger and stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.22,0:27:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This spiritual energy, classically called Kundalini,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.22,0:27:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,shifts brain physiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.22,0:27:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You shift from processing things here on the animal level,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.22,0:27:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the animal level,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.22,0:27:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,which is primarily emotional, emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.22,0:27:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only concerned whether it wants to eat you, attack you, or mate with you, you know?
