Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.19,0:28:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point then in getting all indignant and angry, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.22,0:28:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Or seeking revenge or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.22,0:28:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Because people are reflecting a group karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.78,0:28:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They even tend to congregate on the planet in a similar location.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.72,0:28:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sort of swoop in like birds and settle here,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.03,0:28:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and then these birds swoop in and settle there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.03,0:28:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So below 200 then, which is the animal level,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.14,0:28:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you share with the animals that kind of a karmic propensity
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.25,0:28:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that if you are like a killer of people for the fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.25,0:28:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,then you share the group karma of killers of people for the fun of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.25,0:28:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But not an individual karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.25,0:28:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.83,0:28:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, from 200 up now, you have personal responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.83,0:28:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,because you have an etheric brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.83,0:28:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,which registers all your spiritual decisions,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.83,0:28:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,your yeses and your noses,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.83,0:29:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and you begin to build a spiritual destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.83,0:29:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This brain processes things differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.00,0:29:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Very fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.19,0:29:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Very fast, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.19,0:29:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, this experience of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.19,0:29:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is different than this experience of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.19,0:29:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is New York a friendly place or a hostile place?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.19,0:29:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It all depends on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.74,0:29:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It all depends on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.44,0:29:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My experience of New York is you can stop anybody on the sidewalk anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.44,0:29:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and start a conversation about anything and they'll all have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.44,0:29:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stop anybody and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.44,0:29:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you think of this so-and-so?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.44,0:29:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And the guy says, hey, that's a crock up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.44,0:29:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.44,0:29:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And you met the guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.44,0:29:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and right away you're into comedy with the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.44,0:29:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because of who you are, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.44,0:29:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This person would get paranoid,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.44,0:29:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's probably a pickpocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.44,0:29:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, she'd take her purse and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.44,0:29:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,this gentleman accosted me on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.44,0:29:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She goes, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.44,0:29:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he was just trying to be friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.44,0:30:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So your perception of the world changes
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.44,0:30:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're processing differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.44,0:30:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is crucial.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.44,0:30:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, it's sort of repeated in every book,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.44,0:30:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the most recent books,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.44,0:30:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,because it explains a lot of phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.44,0:30:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and it takes it out of other realms that are more difficult to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.44,0:30:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you see everything is aligned differently than here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.75,0:30:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And the consequences, of course, are quite different
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.98,0:30:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're putting out endorphins.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.98,0:30:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A brain that's dominated by endorphins sees things different
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.98,0:30:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,than a brain dominated by adrenaline and cortisone
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.98,0:30:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and the so-called stress hormones.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.98,0:30:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, we'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.33,0:30:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to do with...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.33,0:30:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It sort of eliminates sociologic theories.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.33,0:30:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's all kinds of sociologic theories
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.33,0:30:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to blame lack of personal responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.33,0:30:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,on all kinds of factors.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.33,0:30:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And we see that the rate of unemployment,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.33,0:30:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of poverty,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.33,0:31:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.33,0:31:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and the rate of criminality
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.33,0:31:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,are all directly, almost exactly,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.33,0:31:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,related to the level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.33,0:31:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.42,0:31:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.65,0:31:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,why pouring money into Haiti does no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.94,0:31:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Haiti, which is into voodoo and black magic and all this,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.94,0:31:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates about 90 or someplace around there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.94,0:31:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And pouring money does no good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.94,0:31:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it makes it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.57,0:31:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so we see that happiness then is
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.57,0:31:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the automatic accompaniment to one's level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.57,0:31:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're very evolved, almost anything can happen
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.57,0:31:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's not going to change your state of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.57,0:31:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, a sociologic import here
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.57,0:31:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is the rate of criminality.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.57,0:31:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The rate of criminality.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.57,0:31:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we see every night on television
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.57,0:31:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,how some judge somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.57,0:31:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,has a recidivist serial killer-raper
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.57,0:32:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and has let the guy go
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.57,0:32:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,because he thinks he's suffering from...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.57,0:32:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to need rehab.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.57,0:32:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to need rehab,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.57,0:32:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but in a different dimension than the human.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.90,0:32:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you calibrate a lot of those criminals,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.90,0:32:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, what's his name, O'Reilly,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.90,0:32:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,he always gets very indignant.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.90,0:32:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He PO'd about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.90,0:32:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody with a terrible thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.90,0:32:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and this judge let him off with, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.90,0:32:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,a small fine or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.90,0:32:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and then two days later he kills somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.90,0:32:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And that just sends O'Reilly up the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.96,0:32:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because they're suffering from a mental disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.96,0:32:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Criminality is a mental disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.96,0:32:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A mental disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.96,0:32:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.96,0:32:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes more than a couple of rehab classes
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.96,0:32:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to recover from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.96,0:32:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I treat a lot of psychopaths,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.96,0:32:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and frankly, the recovery rate was zilch.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.47,0:32:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Pedophiles, the recovery rate was pretty much zilch.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.78,0:32:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, they get arrested for one crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.78,0:32:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'd have them in the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.10,0:33:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say, how many altogether, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.72,0:33:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, 350.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.98,0:33:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's about every 350.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.49,0:33:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.51,0:33:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you've got to have a new boy once a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.51,0:33:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not too often for sex, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.51,0:33:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Once a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.51,0:33:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to the park, go to the kindergarten,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.51,0:33:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you get one kid a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.51,0:33:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end of the year, that's 50 kids, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.51,0:33:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end of three years, you've got 150.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.51,0:33:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So the average guy before a judge
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.90,0:33:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,has done hundreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.90,0:33:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hundreds, hundreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.90,0:33:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So when the judge releases them,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.90,0:33:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you're just releasing another predator on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.90,0:33:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.90,0:33:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The recidivism rate here
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.90,0:33:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,is close to 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.90,0:33:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.38,0:33:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They are dominated by a certain energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.38,0:33:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That energy field may be 10, 20,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.38,0:33:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,or 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.57,0:33:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, dominated by an energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.57,0:33:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,they have group karma of 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.57,0:33:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All the child, serial killers, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.57,0:33:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate around 30, around in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.79,0:33:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.79,0:34:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.14,0:34:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,most of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.14,0:34:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,pedophilia, will go to the park
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.14,0:34:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the day they're released in jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.13,0:34:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The day.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.51,0:34:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They get out at 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.51,0:34:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,By 5, they're in the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.51,0:34:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,See, that's addiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.51,0:34:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Craving this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.51,0:34:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What does an Elkie do who's at forced sobriety?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.51,0:34:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do when you let him out of jail?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.51,0:34:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He heads for the nearest bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.51,0:34:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think he does?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.51,0:34:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.03,0:34:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is diagnostic scale,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.03,0:34:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think the usefulness of it is considerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.26,0:34:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We certainly see it in today's world.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.26,0:34:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just do Iran for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.26,0:34:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if we've got permission to do Iran.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.73,0:34:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got permission to do Iran.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.92,0:34:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.65,0:34:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have been doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.88,0:34:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, people will begin to think
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.26,0:34:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's due to religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.13,0:35:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.34,0:35:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Misconceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.34,0:35:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got nothing to do with religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.34,0:35:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with the leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.34,0:35:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.34,0:35:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.34,0:35:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the three things we have to get
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.34,0:35:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is the leader, the people,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.34,0:35:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.34,0:35:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the people, there's the government,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.34,0:35:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and the leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.34,0:35:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And there can be quite a disparity.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.34,0:35:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have lovely people
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.34,0:35:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,who have been taken over by a dictator.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.34,0:35:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have lovely people,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.34,0:35:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but their whole government is rotten to the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.34,0:35:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And $5 will buy you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.34,0:35:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have to know,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.34,0:35:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to put the three together.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.34,0:35:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think this is useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.34,0:35:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was a diplomat,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.34,0:35:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the first thing I'd want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.34,0:35:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to talk to people from here
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.34,0:35:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,about this subject here,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.34,0:35:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is where I am about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.34,0:35:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where the Republicans are,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.34,0:35:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the Democrats, the President.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.34,0:35:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.34,0:35:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have a staggering amount of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.34,0:36:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't make any mistakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.34,0:36:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,because you know exactly who you're dealing with
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.34,0:36:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and what level,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.34,0:36:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and you know what their expectation is on that level.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.34,0:36:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't make ridiculous comments
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.34,0:36:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and make a fool out of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.34,0:36:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So world leaders very often
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.34,0:36:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,make absolute fools out of themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.34,0:36:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,because they have no idea of credibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.34,0:36:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't know who they're talking to.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.34,0:36:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't understand the American psyche,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.34,0:36:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,because a lot of things they say
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.34,0:36:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to us are ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.34,0:36:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And on the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.34,0:36:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't understand their psyche either.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.34,0:36:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, democracy probably sounds
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.34,0:36:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,idiotic to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.34,0:36:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagine democracy
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.34,0:36:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,sounds like the stupidest fool idea
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.34,0:36:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that you could think of,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.34,0:36:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and we want them to buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.34,0:36:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should they buy it when it's stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.34,0:36:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So the lack of communication
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.34,0:36:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is lack of awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.34,0:36:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of where each person is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.50,0:36:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, as a psychiatrist,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.50,0:36:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,when a new patient walked into my office,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.50,0:36:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it was up to me to know where they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.50,0:36:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It was up to me to intuit,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.53,0:36:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to know, to verify.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.53,0:37:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to know who you're talking to
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.78,0:37:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and at what stage they are
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.78,0:37:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,with various issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.78,0:37:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I suggested AA to a guy
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.78,0:37:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,at this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.78,0:37:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,he would have walked out of the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.78,0:37:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I wait until later,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.78,0:37:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and now I've got him softened up
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.78,0:37:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and now if I suggest it,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.78,0:37:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,he thinks it's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.78,0:37:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So timing depends on your estimation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.86,0:37:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And a lot of political disasters,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.86,0:37:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,diplomatic disasters,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.86,0:37:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,poor timing, very poor timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.86,0:37:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And you hear it every night,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.86,0:37:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,very poor timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.86,0:37:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, with no preparation for the listener.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.86,0:37:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're thinking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.86,0:37:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't democracy wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.17,0:37:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The be-all, end-all of American life
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.17,0:37:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is democracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.17,0:37:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But a large part of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.48,0:37:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,thinks it's stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.48,0:37:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And they just don't wave flags
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.48,0:37:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,with excitement
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.48,0:37:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,when we offer them democracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.48,0:37:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.48,0:37:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The levels of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.48,0:37:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here in the percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.48,0:38:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,As you see at the very bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.48,0:38:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the chances of being happy or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.48,0:38:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Down at the bottom, I guess the happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.48,0:38:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is the thought you're going to be leaving this world soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.53,0:38:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.53,0:38:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So the rate of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.53,0:38:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Even at pride, you get 22%.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.53,0:38:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can see why people,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.53,0:38:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,many people are unwilling to let go
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.53,0:38:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of their anger or their pride
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.53,0:38:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,because at least 12 or 22% of people
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.53,0:38:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,are getting a good deal
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.53,0:38:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of feedback from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.53,0:38:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But then you jump from happiness rate
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.53,0:38:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of 22% to 55%
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.53,0:38:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the minute you go over level 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.53,0:38:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute you go over an integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.53,0:38:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you go up,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.53,0:38:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of happiness becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.53,0:38:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,more and more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.53,0:38:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And over here, the reason it's not higher
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.53,0:38:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is I think because they are self,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.09,0:38:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,their expectation of self
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.09,0:38:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is holding back their sense of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.09,0:38:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That their spiritual goals
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.09,0:38:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,have not been reached
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.09,0:38:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and they,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.09,0:39:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,they're not into a state
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.09,0:39:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of ecstasy and joy yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.11,0:39:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll move on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.01,0:39:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is important because
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.01,0:39:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,what we started with today
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.01,0:39:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,are false teachings, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.01,0:39:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And in all of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.01,0:39:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see the profound gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.01,0:39:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The gain, the sense of power over others,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.01,0:39:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,control, theatrics,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.01,0:39:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the narcissistic ego
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.01,0:39:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,just having a wonderful time,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.01,0:39:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,titles, you know, Grand Master
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.01,0:39:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and this and that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.01,0:39:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.53,0:39:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is very,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.53,0:39:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,for the safety of students,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.53,0:39:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,this is really for everyone's safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.53,0:39:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you get involved with,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.53,0:39:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,see where it lines up
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.53,0:39:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and where it might have a defect.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.53,0:39:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,An organization might be good,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.53,0:39:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,except if you,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.53,0:39:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,if you try to leave it,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.53,0:39:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,they put a rattlesnake in your mailbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.53,0:39:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That would sort of make you think twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.53,0:39:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Which historically is a fact, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.61,0:39:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.05,0:40:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,no requirements or demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.05,0:40:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No membership, no oaths,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.05,0:40:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,no swearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.05,0:40:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to sign anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.05,0:40:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No rules or conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.05,0:40:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Free to come and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.05,0:40:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher has no interest in
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.05,0:40:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the trivia of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.26,0:40:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, sex, lives, economics,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.26,0:40:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,family patterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.26,0:40:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because you're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.26,0:40:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,a level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.26,0:40:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and not the linear domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.26,0:40:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about the non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.48,0:40:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Integrity of purpose,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.48,0:40:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,availability, non-exclusive.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.48,0:40:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, many of the things
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.48,0:40:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that calibrate negative
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.48,0:40:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,are secret ancient mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.48,0:40:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the glamorization
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.48,0:40:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of calling it an ancient mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.48,0:40:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh, an ancient mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.48,0:40:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.73,0:40:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.50,0:40:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You want an ancient vehicle?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.50,0:40:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How about an oxcart, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.90,0:40:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You want ancient communication?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.90,0:40:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thump, thump, thump, thump, thump, thump, thump.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.90,0:41:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoke signals.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.19,0:41:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You want ancient science?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.19,0:41:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You want ancient medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.25,0:41:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a medicine man
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.25,0:41:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,doing brain surgery on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.36,0:41:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You want an ancient mechanic fixing your car?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.28,0:41:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you the truth about ancient.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.28,0:41:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.17,0:41:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Uneducated. Ignorant.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.36,0:41:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, what is so wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.36,0:41:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,about a Stone Age guy's idea
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.36,0:41:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,about the universe?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.03,0:41:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He thinks the stars are God.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.03,0:41:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a good start.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.13,0:41:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wouldn't want to be constrained
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.34,0:41:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,by his knowledge of astronomy
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.34,0:41:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,or anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.34,0:41:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why in a lot of
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.34,0:41:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,other cultures,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.34,0:41:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,what you have is the mythology
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.34,0:41:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,of a primitive culture
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.34,0:41:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,which itself is extremely ignorant.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.82,0:41:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about cultures
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.82,0:41:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,where nobody could read.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.82,0:41:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody went to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.82,0:42:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody even hardly knew arithmetic
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.94,0:42:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,other than the abacus.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.57,0:42:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So what can come out of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.57,0:42:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What can come out of that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.57,0:42:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the ancient myths
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.57,0:42:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and cultural stories
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.57,0:42:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,serve for a sense of
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.57,0:42:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,interpretation.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.57,0:42:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And they subtly have a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.57,0:42:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of them subtly have a lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.57,0:42:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,within them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.57,0:42:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So the purpose is not whether
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.57,0:42:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the story is literally true or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.57,0:42:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether Jonah was actually swallowed
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.57,0:42:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,by a whale is actually irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.73,0:42:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.38,0:42:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so these are the basic
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.38,0:42:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,requirements of any
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.38,0:42:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual organization
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.38,0:42:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,or teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.38,0:42:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is to protect the student
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.38,0:42:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,from being seduced, savaged,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.38,0:42:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and raped.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.38,0:42:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual rape is far more
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.38,0:42:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,painful and devastating
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.50,0:42:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,than physical rape.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.50,0:42:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Physical rape is nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.73,0:42:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,compared to spiritual rape.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.78,0:43:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual rape causes an injury,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.78,0:43:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,a devastation,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.78,0:43:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,which goes on often for decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.78,0:43:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.94,0:43:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.94,0:43:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the exposure of faith,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.94,0:43:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,faith,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.94,0:43:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to put faith in this person
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.94,0:43:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is devastating.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.98,0:43:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've treated people
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.98,0:43:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,who've had that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.98,0:43:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,As I say, the first one I met
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.98,0:43:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,was by a local teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.98,0:43:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,who had fallen down.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.98,0:43:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I met her,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.98,0:43:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,she was on six Prozac a day
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.98,0:43:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep her from suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.34,0:43:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Six Prozac.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.34,0:43:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The devastation of spiritual rape
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.34,0:43:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is horrendous.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.34,0:43:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, do not take a risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.36,0:43:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not take a risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.36,0:43:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't think that because
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.36,0:43:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not devoted,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.36,0:43:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,then you deified the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.36,0:43:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's like you've just gotten
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.36,0:43:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,raped by God in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.36,0:43:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a savage disillusionment.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.59,0:43:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's something you want
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.82,0:43:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to have happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.82,0:44:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So the simplest way is to avoid
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.82,0:44:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it in the first place
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.82,0:44:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,by watching all these things
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.82,0:44:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,which are predictive.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.15,0:44:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.15,0:44:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want the bad karma
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.15,0:44:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of having failed to say
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.15,0:44:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,what I've just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.19,0:44:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to say
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.19,0:44:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that I've had personal experience
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.19,0:44:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as clinical experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.19,0:44:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So I know where I'm speaking
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.19,0:44:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've also calibrated
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.21,0:44:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,all these various cults, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.21,0:44:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.21,0:44:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to safeguard the students,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.21,0:44:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,we have the spiritual teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.21,0:44:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I supposed to look at my watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.46,0:44:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.46,0:44:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.26,0:44:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.26,0:44:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So here's all the great ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.96,0:44:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They're listed for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.96,0:44:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They're verified, authenticated.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.96,0:44:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know the minute I say this
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.96,0:45:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get an email.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.96,0:45:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about Swami Puchadangabhoju?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.01,0:45:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He always calibrates 190.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.01,0:45:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what it is the minute
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.01,0:45:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see the email come through.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.15,0:45:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if he was really in tigris
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.15,0:45:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,why would you have a doubt
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.15,0:45:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and want to know what he calibrates at?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.15,0:45:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And where did you get this guy
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.38,0:45:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,out of a corner?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.38,0:45:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He got over 100 of the greatest
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.38,0:45:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,teachers of all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.38,0:45:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Puchikuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.01,0:45:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.01,0:45:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,First do this hundred,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.01,0:45:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,then send me the email about
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.01,0:45:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Swami Puchiduchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.03,0:45:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who may well be on the other side
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.03,0:45:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to make it even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.63,0:45:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,God help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.63,0:45:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get done with these
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.05,0:45:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,then give me an email.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.05,0:45:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I get the weird ones
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.46,0:45:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,from all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.78,0:45:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now we go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.78,0:45:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I just say that because you can see
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.94,0:46:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm consistent in the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.94,0:46:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If I tell you a hundred easy ways
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.94,0:46:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to get to the North Pole
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.94,0:46:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and you telegraph me from
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.94,0:46:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Puchikanda, Kokum, Mangarok
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.94,0:46:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you didn't want to get to
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.67,0:46:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the North Pole, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.67,0:46:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I already gave you 42 ways to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.67,0:46:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're up to something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.67,0:46:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'll have to look in yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.67,0:46:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and say, what is the something else
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.67,0:46:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm into
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.38,0:46:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,where I'm avoiding the obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.38,0:46:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're avoiding the obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.38,0:46:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you avoiding the obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.38,0:46:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're looking for
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.38,0:46:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,an easy, sure, established pathway
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.38,0:46:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to find something
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.38,0:46:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,unique and exotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.38,0:46:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's probably a karmic proclivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.82,0:46:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the attraction and aversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.82,0:46:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We said that everything
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.46,0:46:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,sticks where it sticks
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.46,0:46:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,because of two sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.46,0:46:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,One is it has a payoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.46,0:46:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the attraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.46,0:46:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And the aversion is
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.46,0:46:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,what would come up if you let it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.46,0:47:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What would come up if you let it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.82,0:47:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So here's the attraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.82,0:47:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's what you're afraid may come up
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.82,0:47:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,if you let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.82,0:47:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And here again is the attraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.82,0:47:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's what's going to come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.82,0:47:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing that comes up when you let go
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.07,0:47:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,a level is the one that's below it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.07,0:47:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.07,0:47:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Like anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.26,0:47:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Underneath anger is somebody just hurt your feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.26,0:47:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and so you're really,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.26,0:47:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you're from his pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.26,0:47:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were humble, you wouldn't have had hurt feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.26,0:47:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,so now you wouldn't be angered, so you wouldn't be thinking about revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.26,0:47:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,See what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.26,0:47:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you feel depressed
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.26,0:47:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,so you see the whole stack.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.26,0:47:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You pull out one toothpick.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.26,0:47:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.40,0:47:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick up sticks we used to play as kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.69,0:47:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You pull out this one stick
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.69,0:47:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and it all collapses.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.69,0:47:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So the secret of rather rapid spiritual evolution
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.69,0:47:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is to see these are all
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.69,0:47:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,sticks and that when you pull one out
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.69,0:47:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole bunch of them
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.69,0:47:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,will collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.69,0:47:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.36,0:48:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so we'll go to the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.82,0:48:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Diagnostic differential.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.82,0:48:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Passion versus love.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.82,0:48:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is one that was sort of popular
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.82,0:48:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,with quite a few people.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.82,0:48:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The quality of love itself
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.82,0:48:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is attracted to passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.82,0:48:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that passion and attraction
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.82,0:48:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates about 145.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.82,0:48:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore it's an
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.82,0:48:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,animal instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.82,0:48:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, frantic to mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.82,0:48:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Like in heat,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.15,0:48:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,frantic, frantic, frantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.30,0:48:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You see it in the nature
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.30,0:48:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.44,0:48:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,These two animals telling each other
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.44,0:48:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is for the frantic desire
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.44,0:48:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.44,0:48:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea is that
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.44,0:48:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so they will see that their progeny
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.44,0:48:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,propagate.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.44,0:48:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's teleologic thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.82,0:48:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The bull just isn't interested
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.82,0:48:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in offspring.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.82,0:48:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He just wants the mate for Christ's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.82,0:48:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not trying to establish
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.98,0:48:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,his genetic line.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.98,0:49:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The crap that gets projected
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.98,0:49:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.98,0:49:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This bull just wants that cow
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.98,0:49:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.98,0:49:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He don't give a damn about genes
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.98,0:49:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,or carrying on his genetic line.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.98,0:49:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all academic
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.98,0:49:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,foolie fool projected onto it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.98,0:49:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.98,0:49:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody who hangs onto shame
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.98,0:49:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,should be ashamed of himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.26,0:49:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.42,0:49:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up all this self-punitive
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.42,0:49:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.42,0:49:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes what you do is
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.42,0:49:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,put yourself into a position
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.42,0:49:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,where others will do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.42,0:49:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you can blame them.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.42,0:49:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, you're the one that
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.42,0:49:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,precipitated that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.61,0:49:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You dropped the hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.61,0:49:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the gossip is out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.61,0:49:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can blame them for being gossips.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.61,0:49:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.90,0:50:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.46,0:50:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Guilt and hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.46,0:50:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, we see guilt is
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.46,0:50:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,expiative in our own fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.46,0:50:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatred is self-propagating.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.46,0:50:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatred is self-propagating.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.46,0:50:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, as we see,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.46,0:50:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,one reason the calibration level
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.46,0:50:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of the world has gone down
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.46,0:50:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is because hatred has become
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.46,0:50:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so widespread
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.46,0:50:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and socially acceptable and approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.46,0:50:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Socially acceptable and approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.46,0:50:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in our own politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.46,0:50:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatred,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.46,0:50:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,especially of the leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.46,0:50:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.46,0:50:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When you accept hatred
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.46,0:50:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,as normal
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.46,0:50:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and even encourage it
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.46,0:50:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,by also
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.46,0:50:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,all kinds of publicity, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.46,0:50:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can make millions of dollars
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.46,0:50:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in today's world with hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.46,0:50:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can get yourself on the cover of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.46,0:50:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and make millions
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.46,0:50:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,within a matter of weeks
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.46,0:50:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,by hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.46,0:50:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So naturally, people would not want to let go of hatred
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.46,0:50:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's their old claim to fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.46,0:51:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so we'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.46,0:51:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Blame, of course, is the underpinning
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.46,0:51:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of social maladjustment.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.50,0:51:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That black comedian
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.50,0:51:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,who lectures to the kids
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.50,0:51:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,about letting go of blame
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.50,0:51:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and taking responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.61,0:51:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Cosby, great guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.55,0:51:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, you see how welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.55,0:51:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,his message is.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.55,0:51:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How much more fun it is
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.55,0:51:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to be able to blame and hate
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.55,0:51:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the supposed cause of your problems
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.55,0:51:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that's out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.55,0:51:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He calls them up on it
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.55,0:51:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's got the courage to face the flak.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.55,0:51:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got the courage to face the flak.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.55,0:51:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He knew he was going to pull out a flak
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.55,0:51:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but he doesn't anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.55,0:51:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's worried about the soul
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.55,0:51:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's worried about the soul of these kids
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.55,0:51:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and current popularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.55,0:51:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's a very demispiritually
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.55,0:51:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,integrous kind of guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.61,0:51:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Apathy, of course, is very difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.61,0:51:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,for people to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.61,0:51:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, as a psychiatrist
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.61,0:52:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw this in severe
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.61,0:52:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,expressions
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.94,0:52:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of self-pity
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.94,0:52:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and helplessness
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.94,0:52:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and just laying down.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.15,0:52:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And we saw this so much
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.15,0:52:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,after major catastrophes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.15,0:52:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Major catastrophes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.17,0:52:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,People into helplessness
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.17,0:52:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and then into rage
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.17,0:52:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,over the fact that
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.17,0:52:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,others didn't do for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.17,0:52:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The time to plan for catastrophe
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.36,0:52:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.36,0:52:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, the most recent poll shows
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.36,0:52:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that even after that
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.36,0:52:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,most of the big cities in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.36,0:52:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,are still not ready for a catastrophe.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.36,0:52:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if there ever will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.42,0:52:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because you've got to use common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.61,0:52:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Grief, we see
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.48,0:52:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,when we say we want to get rid of grief
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.48,0:52:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet there is, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.48,0:52:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the classic stages of grief
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.48,0:52:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,by that psychiatrist
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.48,0:52:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,whose name I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.48,0:52:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger, resentment,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.48,0:53:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,bargaining, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.38,0:53:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, quickly, the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.38,0:53:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The dualities of grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.38,0:53:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dualities of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.48,0:53:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They all have a big payoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.48,0:53:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.73,0:53:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got all of them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.65,0:53:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.07,0:53:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.69,0:53:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,After pride, what have we got?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.53,0:53:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Comparative dualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.76,0:53:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, they're held in place
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.76,0:53:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,by a desire
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.76,0:53:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and also
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.76,0:53:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,by its opposite of a fear
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.76,0:53:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,if we let them go.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.76,0:53:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm not greedy, won't I be poor?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.76,0:53:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm not looking to win all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.76,0:53:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,won't I lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.76,0:53:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, we'll move to the next one
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.76,0:53:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,because we're going to have a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.76,0:53:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The true nature of reality, of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.61,0:53:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In today's world, what can the modern mind
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.61,0:53:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,believe about religion and spiritual reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.61,0:53:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual reality
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.69,0:53:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,in modern man is the name of it
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.69,0:54:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.09,0:54:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,if we go back to see what validity
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.09,0:54:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is available
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.09,0:54:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to anyone in today's world,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.09,0:54:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,we can see what degree of confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.09,0:54:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, for faith
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.51,0:54:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,there should be confidence
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.51,0:54:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that confidence should be into something
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.51,0:54:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,verifiably
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.51,0:54:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore we've published
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.51,0:54:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,pretty much as close as I can get
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.51,0:54:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to the true integrity
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.51,0:54:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,for
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.51,0:54:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever good it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.51,0:54:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.57,0:54:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Does God exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.57,0:54:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we use consciousness research
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.57,0:54:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and we see that all references
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.69,0:54:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to God are infinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.69,0:54:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That sort of does settle the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.01,0:54:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that the great avatars
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.01,0:54:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate really at a thousand
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.01,0:54:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but in their essence at infinity
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.01,0:54:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.01,0:54:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,we verify
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.01,0:54:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,for a modern man who's scientific
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.01,0:54:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,scientific, logical,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.01,0:54:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.01,0:55:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He says, why should I believe in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.01,0:55:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We say, well, this is the verification
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.01,0:55:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,of the truth of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.01,0:55:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so we'll move on, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.01,0:55:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A thousand and the highest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.01,0:55:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are the great spiritual teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.01,0:55:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,which we've repeated in a couple of books
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.01,0:55:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll move on so that people
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.01,0:55:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,don't fall into falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.05,0:55:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is, we could spend this course
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.05,0:55:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,quite a bit of time on this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.11,0:55:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Other teaching schools and traditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.11,0:55:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Body work.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.11,0:55:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the kind of thing
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.11,0:55:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that almost everybody has gotten involved with
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.11,0:55:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're into the spiritual world.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.11,0:55:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of us have checked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.11,0:55:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, agnosticism maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.11,0:55:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and archangel channelers.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.11,0:55:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We've looked at astrology,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.11,0:55:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,biofeedback, body work.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.11,0:55:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We've done workshops
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.11,0:55:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,on codependency.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.11,0:55:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We've played with crystals.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.11,0:55:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotten readings.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.11,0:55:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And we checked out Ekenkar and Est
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.11,0:55:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and we did all these ethical culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.11,0:55:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Feng Shui.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.11,0:55:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got mirrors and things
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.11,0:55:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,around the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.11,0:56:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Rearranged the garden
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.11,0:56:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and different flow lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.11,0:56:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We've all done yoga.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.11,0:56:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We tried holotropic.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.11,0:56:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all the stuff we did, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.11,0:56:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We did the I Ching.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.11,0:56:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Checked out the keys of Enoch.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.26,0:56:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Checked out photography.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.26,0:56:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we do Kung Fu and numerology?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.26,0:56:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we all do Qigong?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.26,0:56:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody got rebirthed and did Reiki
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.26,0:56:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and got Rolfed.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.26,0:56:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you guys do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.69,0:56:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody here didn't get Rolfed?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.00,0:56:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Check out the White Brotherhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.00,0:56:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Check out white magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.00,0:56:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And Wu Din.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.00,0:56:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what that Wu Din is,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.00,0:56:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's one I missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.42,0:56:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I'd missed something.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.42,0:56:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to do Wu Din now
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.42,0:56:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so that I've done Wu Din
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.42,0:56:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and clear off this whole stack.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.42,0:56:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, one more and then we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.42,0:56:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Secularism at 185, 165
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.42,0:56:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is of course the threat
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.42,0:56:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,with relativism.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.21,0:56:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Relativism is the leading edge
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.21,0:57:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,by which secularism takes over.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.21,0:57:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.28,0:57:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The left behind apocalyptic ideology
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.28,0:57:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is quite popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.28,0:57:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They sell a lot of books.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.28,0:57:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But we see that it is predictions of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.28,0:57:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've done most of these before.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.28,0:57:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll move on to the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.28,0:57:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we'll move on to the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.28,0:57:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.44,0:57:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,move on to the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.55,0:57:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,These are merely confirmations
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.90,0:57:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of higher spiritual states.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.90,0:57:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As a scientist,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.90,0:57:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I like to see validation
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.90,0:57:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of the claims of any field.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.90,0:57:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I like to see it validated
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.90,0:57:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,by another field.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.90,0:57:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I like to see one field validated
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.92,0:57:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,by another discipline
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.92,0:57:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that comes in and says,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.92,0:57:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,yes, that is so.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.92,0:57:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I get a kick out of that
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.01,0:57:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,physicist, advanced theoretical physics,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.01,0:57:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,when he grasped that time
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.01,0:57:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and space, etc.,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.01,0:57:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,are all predictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.01,0:57:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like we confirm back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.01,0:58:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't written them yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.01,0:58:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but I probably will.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.15,0:58:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we quit now?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.15,0:58:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we have questions and answers?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.25,0:58:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We get another break.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.25,0:58:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they're wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.50,0:58:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful group.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.38,0:58:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wonderful group, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.38,0:58:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.57,0:58:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very, very fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.61,0:58:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, folks,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.61,0:58:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,we tell the Creative Life Center
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.61,0:58:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is having somebody else come in
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.71,0:58:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,after we leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.86,0:58:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So we've been requested to be prompt
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.86,0:58:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,when we leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.86,0:58:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're going to cut off at 5 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.86,0:58:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.86,0:58:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,if you have a question,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.94,0:58:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't have time
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.94,0:58:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to hear your life story.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.65,0:58:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Try and distill it
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.65,0:59:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to a statement or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.65,0:59:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to distill it
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.65,0:59:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to the crux of the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.65,0:59:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And that'll save time.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.65,0:59:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, you'll understand the answer better
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.65,0:59:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,because a lot of times
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.65,0:59:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,a very complicated question,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.65,0:59:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,when I've answered it,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.65,0:59:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I notice they walk away with a dazed look
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.46,0:59:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so they didn't get it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.46,0:59:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.46,0:59:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramesh Balsikar.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.46,0:59:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramesh Balsikar.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.46,0:59:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering if you would calibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.46,0:59:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,his current level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.46,0:59:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.46,0:59:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been following what's happening with him
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.46,0:59:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,on the internet and you're aware of it, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.46,0:59:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Well, that's your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.15,0:59:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you saying that you believe
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.15,0:59:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,he's gone down?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.15,0:59:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You believe he's gone down?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.53,0:59:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I said the answer's already out there
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.53,0:59:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,in E.E. Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.88,0:59:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,W.W.W. Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.88,0:59:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.98,1:00:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew him when.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.55,1:00:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The calibration I had in the book was the when.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.55,1:00:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, I've been
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.69,1:00:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,studying with an organization
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.69,1:00:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,whose, one of whose distinctions
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.69,1:00:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is word creates world
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.69,1:00:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,as language,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.69,1:00:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,as a way of manifesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.69,1:00:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering if you could...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.69,1:00:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Word creates world.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.11,1:00:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you think it comes out of the word?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.11,1:00:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Language.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.42,1:00:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In the beginning, what does it say in Genesis?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.42,1:00:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In the beginning was the word.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.42,1:00:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And the word was God.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.42,1:00:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And the word was with God.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.42,1:00:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so that gives it the background, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.42,1:00:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.42,1:00:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So what about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.57,1:00:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. Word creates world.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.38,1:00:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to argue with Genesis?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.78,1:00:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The beginning was the word.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.46,1:00:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.46,1:01:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself don't believe that that was the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.46,1:01:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Because prior to the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.53,1:01:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,word
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.69,1:01:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,was.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.59,1:01:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the word is God
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.59,1:01:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,expressed as God.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.98,1:01:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Prior to that was the Godhead.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.75,1:01:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.73,1:01:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Prior to that was the Godhead.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.78,1:01:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.09,1:01:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Prior to Genesis.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.09,1:01:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Genesis is the expression
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.09,1:01:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of the potentiality of the Godhead
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.09,1:01:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,into
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.19,1:01:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,expression as existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.98,1:01:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.65,1:01:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,my question refers to music.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.65,1:01:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When calibrating
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.65,1:01:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the right form of music to listen to,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.65,1:01:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,what are you basing
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.65,1:01:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the calibration on?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.65,1:02:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The form, the sound,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.65,1:02:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the musical composer, the notes?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.65,1:02:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You can break it down if you like.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.98,1:02:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I just ask, what is the overall impact of it?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.98,1:02:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I've also,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.98,1:02:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in Truth vs. False,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.98,1:02:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,with calibrated composers,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.98,1:02:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you can calibrate composer
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.98,1:02:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and music, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.11,1:02:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never broke it down that much.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.11,1:02:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the music we play here
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.11,1:02:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at 700.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.11,1:02:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And the author of that is
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.82,1:02:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Robert Gass.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.36,1:02:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Robert Gass.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.36,1:02:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't break it down into him as a person
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.36,1:02:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,or individual.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.36,1:02:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the impact?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.36,1:02:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the impact of La Boheme?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.36,1:02:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.98,1:02:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does La Boheme make you cry?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.98,1:02:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, it always makes me cry.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.71,1:02:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a gift for you for Father's Day, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.71,1:02:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't that nice?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.71,1:02:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that nice?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.71,1:02:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tim Russert is the author
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.71,1:02:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,in Wisdom of Our Fathers.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.71,1:02:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sounds great.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.71,1:03:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, because we're talking about
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.21,1:03:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the wisdom of oligarchy today.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.21,1:03:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Salvation of mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.21,1:03:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is in wisdom, not in political positionality.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.17,1:03:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The first year that I was
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.30,1:03:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,coming here, everything was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.30,1:03:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Insights, joyous.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.30,1:03:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've been getting worse ever since, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.30,1:03:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.30,1:03:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you getting worse?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.30,1:03:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then I went through
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.30,1:03:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,one issue.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.50,1:03:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My whole life was just about one issue.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.50,1:03:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Very intense, lots of pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.50,1:03:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Prayer, which helped.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.84,1:03:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And then one day,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.84,1:03:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,just clear, was gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.84,1:03:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt it actually leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.84,1:03:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The intensity.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.94,1:03:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So is that a stack?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.94,1:03:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a stack.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.94,1:03:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we think is
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.98,1:03:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the cause of pain
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.98,1:03:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in this lifetime
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.98,1:03:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is a whole stack of the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.98,1:03:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you experience in this lifetime
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.98,1:03:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is the uncorking of the whole stack.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.98,1:04:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Est
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.19,1:04:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,did a good job of teaching that.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.19,1:04:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Est?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.19,1:04:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That you're pulling up a stack.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.19,1:04:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, they call them
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.19,1:04:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,ones, twos, and threes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.19,1:04:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Depending on how big
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.19,1:04:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and bad a stack it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.19,1:04:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you pull up a stack
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.19,1:04:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and what you didn't realize
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.19,1:04:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is you pulled up a big stack.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.28,1:04:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,From other lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.28,1:04:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.82,1:04:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You pulled up a big stack.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.21,1:04:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.21,1:04:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I'm picking up something
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.21,1:04:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,from the aura
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.21,1:04:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,of some other person.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.21,1:04:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want to know
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.21,1:04:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,how to best protect yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.21,1:04:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,or clean it up if it happens
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.21,1:04:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and how careful?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.21,1:04:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do the thymic thump.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.21,1:04:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.21,1:04:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What I do is
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.38,1:04:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,if I'm not aware of what something is
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.38,1:05:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,then I can't quite put my finger on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.38,1:05:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask the Holy Spirit for a miracle
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.38,1:05:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to reveal to me the truth of that
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.38,1:05:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,which I am puzzling about.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.38,1:05:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I leave it alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.44,1:05:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And then in the middle of a peanut butter sandwich
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.44,1:05:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I suddenly get out.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.40,1:05:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How careful should you be
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.40,1:05:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,with other people?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.40,1:05:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you said one time
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.40,1:05:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in this lecture.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.40,1:05:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go to the new age festivals
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.40,1:05:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but in general
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.40,1:05:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean like normal people.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.40,1:05:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What was he asking me?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.40,1:05:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Avoid them.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.40,1:05:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Avoid the new age.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.40,1:05:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you don't know what you're getting into.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.40,1:05:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, but other people
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.40,1:05:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,have also negative karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.40,1:05:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How much should you avoid?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.40,1:05:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Should you just stay in your room?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.40,1:05:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How should you avoid it?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.40,1:05:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Should you just isolate yourself or what?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.61,1:05:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.61,1:05:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Because a lot of people
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.98,1:05:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Like even normal people
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.98,1:05:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,have something.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.98,1:06:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even normal people have something.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.98,1:06:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is the question?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.03,1:06:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you protect yourself?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.03,1:06:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,From what? Other people's negative energies?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.03,1:06:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.03,1:06:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you cleared that in yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.03,1:06:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and transcended it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.23,1:06:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've got to have a hook
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.23,1:06:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that they can put it in.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.23,1:06:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So once you've cleared that out
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.23,1:06:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,then that hook doesn't remain anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.23,1:06:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's really just as myself
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.23,1:06:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,as my issue and that's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.86,1:06:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can clear the energy
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.84,1:06:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,quickly by the thymic thump, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.84,1:06:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But you still don't know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.84,1:06:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can use kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.84,1:06:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to find out what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.84,1:06:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use intuition.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.84,1:06:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can ask the Holy Spirit for a miracle
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.96,1:06:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that it be revealed to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.96,1:06:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.21,1:07:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.73,1:07:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.73,1:07:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,what the nervousness
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.26,1:07:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,what comes up
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.26,1:07:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,when you look into somebody's eyes
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.26,1:07:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,because there's very few
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.59,1:07:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,people I can look into their eyes
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.59,1:07:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,except for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.51,1:07:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What comes up in people's eyes?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.51,1:07:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.51,1:07:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a real strong connection?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.51,1:07:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well what comes up is the self
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.51,1:07:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,reflected back to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.51,1:07:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was in psychiatric practice
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.51,1:07:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I wrote about they would bring
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.51,1:07:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the most pathetic things from all over the world
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.51,1:07:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,wrapped in wet sheets
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.51,1:07:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,writhing on the floor, grotesque,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.51,1:07:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.28,1:07:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would look into their eyes
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.82,1:07:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and they felt healed in that instant.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.05,1:07:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes the physicality
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.05,1:07:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,did not socially recover
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.05,1:07:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but the person within
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.05,1:07:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,was recovered because
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.05,1:07:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,who they really were had been recognized
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.05,1:07:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and reciprocated.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.05,1:07:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was the moment of the miracle.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.05,1:08:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So many of the recoveries
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.05,1:08:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,were miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.05,1:08:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the self sees the self.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.05,1:08:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That self recognizes the self.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.05,1:08:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.34,1:08:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that was the relief of the sufferer.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.34,1:08:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My only ambition
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.03,1:08:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,was that their suffering be relieved.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.03,1:08:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Their socio-economic
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.03,1:08:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,recovery was not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.03,1:08:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the family's.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.53,1:08:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.27,1:08:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.06,1:08:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been having a little bit of
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.18,1:08:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,troubles juggling
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.18,1:08:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the paradox of not doing
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.18,1:08:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and being completely surrendered
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.18,1:08:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and then not doing enough
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.18,1:08:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to be a diligent follower of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.18,1:08:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was wondering if maybe
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.93,1:08:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you could help me clear it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.47,1:08:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing this is not a block.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.47,1:08:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing this has to do with
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.85,1:08:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,what your mind is doing
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.85,1:09:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,while you're doing this.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.14,1:09:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're doing it from context
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.14,1:09:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not going to interfere.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.14,1:09:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're doing it from content
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.75,1:09:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it's going to be a constant interruption.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.64,1:09:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're just being who you are
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.64,1:09:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,then everything is happening spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.64,1:09:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not interrupting anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.64,1:09:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're trying to do something
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.64,1:09:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,outside of the
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.64,1:09:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you really are
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.64,1:09:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,something artificial
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.64,1:09:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that's going to interrupt you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.64,1:09:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Beheading people all the time
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.64,1:09:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is your job as the headsman
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.64,1:09:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and chopping off a head doesn't bother you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.93,1:09:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.93,1:09:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's just a routine day for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.93,1:09:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How is some?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.93,1:09:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I say that from experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.93,1:09:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A few shekels, Will.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.93,1:09:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.93,1:09:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.93,1:10:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.82,1:10:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a job.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.82,1:10:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't feel guilty for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.82,1:10:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just your job.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.81,1:10:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How can one be kind
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.53,1:10:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and compassionate and loving
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.53,1:10:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet at the same time
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.53,1:10:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,not karmically interfere in other people
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.53,1:10:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and other lives?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.53,1:10:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Good one.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.53,1:10:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be loving
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.69,1:10:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and caring and not interfere
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.69,1:10:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,with someone else's karma?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.69,1:10:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How does being loving interfere with the karma?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.69,1:10:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe you intervene too much
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.69,1:10:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and change...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.69,1:10:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say a child...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.69,1:10:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about being overprotective?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.69,1:10:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If a child is being beaten
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.69,1:10:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're there
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.69,1:10:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and I want to interfere
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.69,1:10:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You automatically respond
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.69,1:10:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,based on your level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.69,1:11:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You might say
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.60,1:11:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the third level is not even happening
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.60,1:11:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,this is just a perceptual illusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.60,1:11:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You might say karmically
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.60,1:11:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,this kid deserves it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.78,1:11:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You might say
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.78,1:11:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it is not my place to intervene in God's world.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.85,1:11:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you may feel called upon
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.85,1:11:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to intervene
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.02,1:11:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in the child's behalf.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.02,1:11:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So it would depend on
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.02,1:11:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,how you define yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.02,1:11:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in this world
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.02,1:11:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and what your function is.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.02,1:11:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My function has always been
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.02,1:11:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,therapeutic.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.02,1:11:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to relieve the suffering of a puppy.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.02,1:11:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As a doctor I want to relieve suffering.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.02,1:11:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And as a spiritual teacher
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.02,1:11:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to prevent and relieve spiritual suffering.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.02,1:11:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's always been my orientation.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.02,1:11:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.02,1:11:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That out of that which you are
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.02,1:11:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you value
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.02,1:11:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you behave out of that which you value.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.07,1:11:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think the relief of suffering
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.07,1:11:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is what I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.07,1:11:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I've always done.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.21,1:11:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.21,1:12:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you call them
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.01,1:12:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that take care of animals?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.19,1:12:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A veterinarian?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.19,1:12:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a vet.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.19,1:12:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be the same as a veterinarian.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.35,1:12:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I could equally be a veterinarian.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.35,1:12:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the relief of suffering
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.35,1:12:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,brings a sense of fulfillment.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.35,1:12:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's a puppy or a human being
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.35,1:12:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,or a poor old lady sitting by herself.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.68,1:12:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.76,1:12:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My question has been answered.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.76,1:12:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But thank you for being my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.76,1:12:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the gift
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.76,1:12:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of being my student.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.92,1:12:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Every student
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.92,1:12:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.50,1:12:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I do this here?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.61,1:12:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.94,1:12:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping you could help me
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.59,1:12:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,with a continuous dream
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.59,1:12:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that I keep having.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.59,1:13:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Dream?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.59,1:13:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that alright?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.59,1:13:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.59,1:13:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I have this dream where
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.59,1:13:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm chewing gum
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.59,1:13:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and I go to spit it out
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.59,1:13:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can't so I use my hand
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.59,1:13:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and I keep on pulling and pulling
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.59,1:13:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it will finally snap
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.59,1:13:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's still some in my mouth
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.59,1:13:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just keep pulling and pulling.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.59,1:13:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of a nightmare for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.65,1:13:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a weird dream, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.03,1:13:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got bubble gum.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.65,1:13:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.65,1:13:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.65,1:13:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it means.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.65,1:13:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,See, in psychoanalysis
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.65,1:13:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you would lay on the couch
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.85,1:13:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and both of us would ignore this
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.85,1:13:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and maybe tomorrow or the next day
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.85,1:13:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,it would suddenly come to you
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.10,1:13:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,what it means, or I would get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.10,1:13:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really a psychoanalytic question
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.10,1:13:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd have to be in psychoanalysis
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.81,1:13:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the two of us would come
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.81,1:13:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,on what it probably means, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.81,1:13:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.81,1:14:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Something sticky, something oral.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.57,1:14:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stuck with my orality.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.57,1:14:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, what is the symbolic language?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.57,1:14:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dreams are always symbolic.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.57,1:14:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The gum's lost its flavor
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.57,1:14:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so I keep on trying to spit it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.57,1:14:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if that makes any difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.57,1:14:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.80,1:14:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You've depleted it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.80,1:14:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's time to stick it under the seat
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.80,1:14:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,for the next one.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.80,1:14:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I didn't really get an answer
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.80,1:14:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,on that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.82,1:14:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ask another question
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.82,1:14:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but you didn't answer now.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.82,1:14:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave you a response.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.82,1:14:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say I was going to answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.82,1:14:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I'd like to remind people
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.82,1:14:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I give you what I know
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.82,1:14:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't claim omniscience.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.82,1:14:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Once in a while people
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.82,1:14:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,hit me for being not omniscient.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.82,1:14:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't claim omniscience
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.38,1:14:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,any more than I come playing
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.38,1:14:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,omnipresence
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.38,1:14:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,or omnipotence.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.38,1:14:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you could help me
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.38,1:14:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,with mudras.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.38,1:15:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could show me a couple different mudras
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.38,1:15:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and what they mean
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.38,1:15:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and when to use them.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.59,1:15:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know that it's something
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.59,1:15:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I necessarily consciously use.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.59,1:15:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A mudra has a hand position.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.59,1:15:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You might say it's symbolic
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.59,1:15:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,languaging.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.72,1:15:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When I say live your life as a prayer
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.72,1:15:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.75,1:15:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that your
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.85,1:15:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,configuration, the way you relate to God
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.85,1:15:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is more or less
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.85,1:15:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,honestly.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.01,1:15:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very yin.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.01,1:15:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The yin position
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.06,1:15:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,in the three-dimensional world
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.06,1:15:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to be very yang
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.14,1:15:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the spiritual world
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.14,1:15:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like yin.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.14,1:15:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You pull by attraction.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.10,1:15:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If I live my life
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.10,1:15:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,as this position to God
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.10,1:15:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,how can he refuse me?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.73,1:15:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life is a supplication.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.18,1:15:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,To thee, O Lord,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.22,1:15:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,do I devote my life
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.69,1:15:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and ask to be a channel
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.69,1:16:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,so that is
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.39,1:16:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,a powerful yin
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.39,1:16:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,attraction.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.48,1:16:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You might say the great beings flock to your side
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.48,1:16:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,because they see
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.96,1:16:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to thee, O Lord,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.96,1:16:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,do I devote my life
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.96,1:16:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that I may be thy servant.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.09,1:16:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very powerful
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.09,1:16:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.09,1:16:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the very powerful yin pull of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.63,1:16:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much. Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.63,1:16:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get a picture real quick?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.69,1:16:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.89,1:16:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.89,1:16:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So much.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.06,1:16:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, I'm glad you brought up
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.06,1:16:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the list of spiritual myths
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.06,1:16:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,right at the beginning. I've read some of those
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.06,1:16:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,books myself. And in the last
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.06,1:16:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,two weeks I ran into one other
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.06,1:16:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,book. It's called The Impersonal
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.06,1:17:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Life by Joseph Benner.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.06,1:17:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't know if you've
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.06,1:17:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,heard of this work. It was written a long
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.06,1:17:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,time ago in 1944 or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.06,1:17:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wrote it?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.06,1:17:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Joseph Benner.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.06,1:17:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not familiar with the book.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.06,1:17:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.77,1:17:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The other thing is I'm
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.77,1:17:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,a doctor and I've been listening
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.77,1:17:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to your lectures, the Health and Healing
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.77,1:17:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,series.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.77,1:17:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And so what advice would you give
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.77,1:17:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,me in my clinic? I'm trying
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.77,1:17:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to bring some of those principles
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.77,1:17:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,for my patients.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.77,1:17:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And it doesn't seem in context
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.77,1:17:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,in where I'm
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.77,1:17:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at data and talking
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.77,1:17:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,about results and so on.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.77,1:17:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet a part of me in some
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.77,1:17:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,situations wants to bring
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.77,1:17:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that into their awareness that
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.77,1:17:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,they need to have inquiry
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.77,1:17:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,as to why they're sick.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.77,1:17:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So how can I bring your principles
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.77,1:17:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,in my practice? What advice
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.77,1:17:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,would you give? What I did was I started
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.77,1:17:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,an attitudinal healing center
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.77,1:17:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,in the clinic in which I was director.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.77,1:18:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So at no charge
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.77,1:18:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,people with hopeless diseases
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.77,1:18:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,could get together and study the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.77,1:18:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So that created
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.77,1:18:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,a spiritual context for healing.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.77,1:18:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And gave them a whole
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.77,1:18:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,new different idea on how they could
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.77,1:18:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,approach it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.77,1:18:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm passing up the
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.77,1:18:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Course in Miracles in my clinic.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.77,1:18:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not being thrown out of my
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.77,1:18:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,work yet. What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.77,1:18:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I do tell my patients
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.77,1:18:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,about a Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.77,1:18:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Telling them about it is one thing, but actually
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.77,1:18:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,supporting it. See, because
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.77,1:18:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll say, yeah, uh-huh, and they won't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.77,1:18:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But if they get together
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.77,1:18:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,one evening a week, pretty soon they form
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.77,1:18:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,a camaraderie. And then they
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.77,1:18:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,begin to see the change in each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.77,1:18:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the miraculous begins to
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.77,1:18:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,occur.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.85,1:18:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.18,1:18:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.18,1:18:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that in here?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.18,1:18:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.32,1:19:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that in here?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.69,1:19:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's science of mind. I forgot I was even
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.69,1:19:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,in science of mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.81,1:19:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.81,1:19:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, we're very grateful
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.81,1:19:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,for your teaching. And when we were here
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.81,1:19:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,last time, you said a number of things
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.81,1:19:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that inspired us to put together
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.81,1:19:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,a bag of gifts of various kinds
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.81,1:19:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,for you and Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.81,1:19:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's a letter
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.81,1:19:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,in there which explains the different
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.81,1:19:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,gifts and how they might
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.81,1:19:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,be used, depending on how kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.81,1:19:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,indicates they might or might not be
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.81,1:19:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,useful for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.81,1:19:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And our birthday wish for you is that
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.81,1:19:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever time you have
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.88,1:19:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,with us in
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.52,1:19:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,service, that it be
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.52,1:19:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,filled with joy and health and strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.52,1:19:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.86,1:19:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that's a beautiful wish.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.86,1:19:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone in the room shares this.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.06,1:20:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a question
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.09,1:20:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,about people who are up,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.09,1:20:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, we've calibrated someone like
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.09,1:20:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother Teresa at 700 or above.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.09,1:20:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And she
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.09,1:20:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,was very, very against
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.09,1:20:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,abortion
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.09,1:20:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and preached quite
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.09,1:20:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,adamantly. She was a Catholic.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.09,1:20:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.09,1:20:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The one time she was
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.10,1:20:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,at 700,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.10,1:20:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the first time I went to hear her speak,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.10,1:20:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,she just talked about how horrible it was
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.10,1:20:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that people had abortions.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.10,1:20:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And then in your book, you've also said
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.10,1:20:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that until the third month,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.10,1:20:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the fetus...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.10,1:20:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's the facts.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.10,1:20:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, that's the facts.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.10,1:20:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I guess I get confused,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.10,1:20:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and you were talking today about
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.10,1:21:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,who do we know how to trust,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.10,1:21:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is that I admire Mother Teresa
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.10,1:21:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.10,1:21:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.10,1:21:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,we should never have abortions.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.10,1:21:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see the question?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.10,1:21:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I get very confused about...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.10,1:21:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, because you have your own individual
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.10,1:21:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual path to evolve through, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.10,1:21:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We give you
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.10,1:21:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the facts, and now what you do with them
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.10,1:21:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,depends on where you're at.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.10,1:21:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be willing to sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.10,1:21:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the benefits of abortion
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.10,1:21:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,in return for
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.10,1:21:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the positive
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.10,1:21:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,karma of having chosen what you
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.10,1:21:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,consider to be the spiritually higher
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.10,1:21:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,path, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.10,1:21:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it may not be the abortion itself,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.10,1:21:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but the intention by which you make the decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.46,1:21:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I merely pointed out the facts
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.46,1:21:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that the spirit doesn't end at the fetus
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.46,1:21:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,until the third month of gestation.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.46,1:21:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So that people who have had abortions
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.46,1:21:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe wouldn't feel quite as guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.46,1:21:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't really kill a spirit, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.46,1:21:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.46,1:21:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I just thought it might help
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.46,1:21:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,clarify, because
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.46,1:22:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any position about it, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.46,1:22:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As a physician, I myself cannot do it,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.46,1:22:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you see. But that's just my own
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.46,1:22:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,position.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.46,1:22:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that different than
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.46,1:22:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,relativism, then?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.46,1:22:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Relativism is a whole different ball game.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.46,1:22:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A ball game?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.46,1:22:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, from relativism
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.06,1:22:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't have any problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.06,1:22:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Because from relativism, there is no right
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.06,1:22:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and wrong. Everybody
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.11,1:22:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is the author of their own moral
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.11,1:22:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,code, and they have no obligation to agree
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.11,1:22:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,with truth or falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.11,1:22:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So a relativist wouldn't be worrying about the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.11,1:22:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, and then
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.01,1:22:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,someone might have a
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.01,1:22:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,different position, say, from you
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.01,1:22:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,or from Mother Teresa, and it isn't
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.01,1:22:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,necessarily the wrong one.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.01,1:22:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're on their own spiritual path.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.01,1:22:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's their choice. The only rule
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.01,1:22:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,we have right now is if we calibrate them.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.01,1:22:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say we calibrate
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.01,1:22:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,this person has an abortion at this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.01,1:22:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that calibrate at?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.01,1:22:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we say, what does it calibrate
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.01,1:23:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to reject an abortion
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.01,1:23:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,from spiritual principles?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.01,1:23:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And now it's up to you to choose.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.46,1:23:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and by the way, it's not because
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.46,1:23:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of having an abortion.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.46,1:23:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That just
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.46,1:23:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,encouraged me. I'm not either, but you're
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.46,1:23:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,presenting me with a hypothetical position.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.46,1:23:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you resolve it? You try to extract
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.46,1:23:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the essence of all of it, and then from that,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.46,1:23:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,depending on where you are, you will make your choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.46,1:23:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.60,1:23:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,then when you are adopting
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.60,1:23:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to follow someone and have
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.60,1:23:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,them be your teacher, you might
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.60,1:23:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,not agree with them on everything?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.60,1:23:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You might not agree with everything, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.60,1:23:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you. Then you should feel
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.02,1:23:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,guilty, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.60,1:23:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to feel guilty about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.60,1:23:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just had to say that.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.81,1:23:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, just you get to the other side
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.89,1:23:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and Mother Teresa greets you,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.89,1:23:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and you discover she's your
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.42,1:23:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,angel on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.42,1:24:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.06,1:24:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of things we do, not out of
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.06,1:24:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,rationality, but out of love.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.06,1:24:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So you might forgo a convenience
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.06,1:24:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,out of love for Mother Teresa.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.06,1:24:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of love, see? So there your motivation
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.06,1:24:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,would be, out of my love
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.06,1:24:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,for this teacher, I will follow
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.06,1:24:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,this teacher's teachings.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.06,1:24:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of love. Not out of fear of
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.22,1:24:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.22,1:24:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you just read my mind and tell me what my question is?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.22,1:24:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.22,1:24:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.22,1:24:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was wondering,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.22,1:24:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I was listening to the lecture
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.22,1:24:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,today, and I had heard you say
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.22,1:24:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that for the pedophilers and things like that,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.22,1:24:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an alcoholic, and I go to
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.22,1:24:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the AA, and I see
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.22,1:24:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that there's been great help, but I know the statistics
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.22,1:24:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is very low as far as recovery
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.22,1:24:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is concerned, but you said there was no hope
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.22,1:24:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,for those people, and
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.22,1:24:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just wondering, because I want... No hope for what?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.22,1:24:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,For alcoholics?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.22,1:24:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, the pedophilers. What's it got to do with the AA?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.22,1:24:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, because I think that everybody has
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.22,1:24:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,a chance, and... Oh, you're coming
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.22,1:24:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,from the hypothetical idealism.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.22,1:25:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.22,1:25:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to use a dictionary to read some
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.22,1:25:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,of your books, so can you...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.22,1:25:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm new
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.22,1:25:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,at this, this is my first conference here,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.22,1:25:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but I mean, what I... I'm just
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.22,1:25:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,giving you a clinical experience. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.22,1:25:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the experience. The only
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.22,1:25:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,cases I ever saw recover from it
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.22,1:25:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,were people who joined a 12-step group
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.22,1:25:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and they were avid members,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.22,1:25:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and those few guys did recover,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.22,1:25:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,at least for the period of time
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.22,1:25:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that I continued to see them.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.22,1:25:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's other groups for people that just aren't
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.22,1:25:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,alcoholic or drug addicts, I mean, there's other...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.22,1:25:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I know there's, like, fat people groups, and
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.22,1:25:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,um...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.22,1:25:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Overeaters Anonymous, and Gambling Anonymous, and...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.22,1:25:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the recovery from pedophilia, the only ones
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.22,1:25:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw had joined AA groups
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.22,1:25:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and practiced the
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.22,1:25:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,principles of all their...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.22,1:25:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess what I'm getting at is that
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.22,1:25:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of curious as to how you got started
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.22,1:25:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,doing this, because I wake up at 3 in the morning
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.22,1:25:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and, you know, my husband's like, what are you doing? Are you high
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.22,1:25:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,or something? I mean, because I get these great ideas
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.22,1:25:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and I want to write Oprah a letter and be on her show
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.22,1:26:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and, you know, and I get real, um, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.22,1:26:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,interested in doing this kind of work
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.22,1:26:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,one day, you know, and helping people, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.22,1:26:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? What?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.38,1:26:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He says yes. What's the question? Oh, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.38,1:26:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get started
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.38,1:26:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,doing this sort of stuff and helping so many people?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.38,1:26:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You want my life story?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.65,1:26:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Just, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.65,1:26:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you... because I have all the ideas in my
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.65,1:26:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,head, but how do you manifest that? I mean,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.65,1:26:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, to just... It's too general
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.65,1:26:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,a question to answer. Sorry. My own life
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.65,1:26:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,was quite complex and also quite unusual,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.65,1:26:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but there are very powerful
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.65,1:26:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,experiences that catapulted me
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.65,1:26:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,into certain states, and
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.65,1:26:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,from that state, you saw everything and understood
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.65,1:26:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,it differently. That's all I can say.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.65,1:26:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Each level of spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.65,1:26:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,evolution, you get a...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.65,1:26:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true. You get a revolution,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.65,1:26:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,an evolution of
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.65,1:26:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,your worldview. It looks different.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.65,1:26:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. And many of the most major
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.65,1:26:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,things that have come to me came to me out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.65,1:26:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't thinking about it. I wasn't contemplating.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.65,1:26:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.65,1:26:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Three in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.65,1:26:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.65,1:27:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess my question is, what do you do after that?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.65,1:27:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, a problem... It becomes obvious
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.65,1:27:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,what to do after that. Yeah. You can't
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.65,1:27:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,answer it from the hypothetical. You have to answer it from
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.65,1:27:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the real. Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.89,1:27:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's meant to be, it'll just come.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.89,1:27:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.94,1:27:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.94,1:27:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I found an article
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.94,1:27:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,a couple months ago in the St. Pete Times
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.94,1:27:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In the what? In St. Pete Times in
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.94,1:27:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Florida, and it was kind of apropos
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.94,1:27:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to the subject today. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.94,1:27:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And the article reads,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.94,1:27:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Scientology, nearly ready
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.94,1:27:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to unveil super power.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.94,1:27:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And the subtitle
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.22,1:27:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is, in the works for decades, the
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.22,1:27:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,closely guarded spiritual training program
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.22,1:27:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,will be revealed in clear water.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.22,1:27:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And so... What's the price?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.39,1:27:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what the price is.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.39,1:27:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tens of thousands
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.39,1:27:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,of dollars. Boy. And so
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.39,1:27:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you the article. It's kind of... They have
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.39,1:27:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,put it on the front page, but I thought...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.39,1:27:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's interesting, yeah. It should be in the entertainment
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.39,1:28:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,section.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.39,1:28:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.03,1:28:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Scientology is the whole study in itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.03,1:28:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Dianetics.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.03,1:28:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. And then what happened to him later in life?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.03,1:28:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, he stayed... He never came near
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.03,1:28:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the shores of the U.S. after that?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.03,1:28:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he was on a ship. He was paranoid. He lived on a ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.03,1:28:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He thought the FBI was after him. Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.03,1:28:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But you
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.19,1:28:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,brought up the name in the lecture
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.19,1:28:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,today. Oh, yes. Because of
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.19,1:28:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the anti-psychiatry
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.19,1:28:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,movement, you know. Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.19,1:28:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Which sounded
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.19,1:28:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,idealistic, but when you look what is the
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.19,1:28:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,consequence, it was disaster
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.19,1:28:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,for millions. And their organization
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.19,1:28:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,has worldwide
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.19,1:28:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,global,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.19,1:28:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, aspirations.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.19,1:28:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering, you've never...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.19,1:28:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In any of your books, you never calibrated the organization.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.19,1:28:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's banned in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.19,1:28:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.19,1:28:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's certain things you'll find
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.19,1:28:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,missing from the book
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.19,1:28:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that you would expect. And I have
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.19,1:29:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,good reasons to omit them.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.19,1:29:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, I don't want a rattlesnake
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.19,1:29:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in my mailbox.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.19,1:29:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They're very litigious.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.19,1:29:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Secondly, I don't want 50 or 100
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.19,1:29:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,lawsuits trying to wear me out just with
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.19,1:29:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the cost of defending lawsuits, which is
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.19,1:29:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the tactic of a certain
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.26,1:29:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,organization, which is also glaringly
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.26,1:29:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,missing. But I think any spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.26,1:29:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,student would get instantly what they
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.26,1:29:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.26,1:29:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Paul. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.52,1:29:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was perfect. I just wouldn't want to be
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.52,1:29:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,any of them at death's door when you think you
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.52,1:29:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,devoted your whole life to eliminating God
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.52,1:29:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,from the human universe,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.52,1:29:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you realize that you're about to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.52,1:29:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a good thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.52,1:29:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. Reality check.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.52,1:29:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.52,1:29:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.52,1:29:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the last thought he had before he left
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.52,1:29:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the world? Oops.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.68,1:29:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He stepped out of the human body
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.86,1:29:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,right into a banana peel.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.97,1:30:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.00,1:30:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I love to paint.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.00,1:30:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You love what? I love painting.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.00,1:30:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want to steward
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.00,1:30:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that love of art and be a working
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.00,1:30:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,artist. And I try to make
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.00,1:30:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the work in a spirit of devotion.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.00,1:30:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But I'm wondering if you could speak some more
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.00,1:30:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,about the spiritual significance
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.00,1:30:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of art and how it can be of service.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.00,1:30:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.00,1:30:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a great and classic study, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.00,1:30:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,from the dome of
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.85,1:30:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,what you call it in the
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.85,1:30:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Vatican.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.85,1:30:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirituality and art, of course,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.85,1:30:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,have been so closely
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.85,1:30:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,in relationship. And art has
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.85,1:30:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,played a very important part throughout
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.85,1:30:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,all the history of religion
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.96,1:30:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and spirituality.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.06,1:30:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So certainly it could
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.06,1:30:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,inspire your work.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.06,1:30:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.77,1:30:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sistine
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.77,1:30:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapel. The ceiling of the Sistine
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.77,1:30:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapel.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.61,1:31:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine what it took
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.61,1:31:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,him to do that. What was it? Four years
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.61,1:31:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,on his back up there. Four years
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.61,1:31:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,on his back. Hanging up
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.61,1:31:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,upside down. Good God.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.97,1:31:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What a
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.06,1:31:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,devotion.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.63,1:31:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.63,1:31:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Four years on your back.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.60,1:31:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We also wonder if we could take a picture with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.60,1:31:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Paint the
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.11,1:31:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,ceiling of the Sistine Chapel.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.11,1:31:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, oh boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.65,1:31:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Doc?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.46,1:31:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking at
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.14,1:31:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the Sistine Chapel in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.14,1:31:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.97,1:31:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Man reaching for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.28,1:31:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.47,1:31:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, I'm going into my last
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.47,1:31:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,year of a psychotherapy program,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.47,1:31:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,a Buddhist-based one. Last year of what?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.47,1:31:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A training in psychotherapy, to be
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.47,1:31:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,a psychotherapist. Oh, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.47,1:32:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And I noticed personally, I have a lot
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.47,1:32:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,of self-interest and attraction to your
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.47,1:32:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,work, this context. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.47,1:32:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And I also noticed kind of two
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.47,1:32:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,things, almost
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.47,1:32:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,like judgment or an aversion
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.47,1:32:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,to working outside
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.47,1:32:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,of it, or I have
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.47,1:32:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,this question, if I'm going to, you mentioned
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.47,1:32:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,timing and like working with
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.47,1:32:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,a client, and you only mention A
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.47,1:32:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,at a certain point to a certain person.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.47,1:32:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're ready for it, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.47,1:32:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So my question is just, and again, I haven't been
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.47,1:32:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing a lot of clients yet, so I'm wondering
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.47,1:32:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,how to bring this context in a meaningful
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.47,1:32:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,way, working
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.47,1:32:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,with someone one-on-one.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.47,1:32:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What you do is, whatever your
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.47,1:32:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,frame of reference is,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.47,1:32:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, you incorporate
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.47,1:32:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that into yourself, and then
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.47,1:32:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you merely explain to the patient
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.47,1:32:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,how you see it from this particular context.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.47,1:32:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,See? And
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.38,1:32:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,with a therapeutic
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.10,1:32:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,intention, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.10,1:32:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.30,1:32:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I incorporated information from
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.30,1:33:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,a variety of sources, Freud,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.30,1:33:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Jung, brain
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.30,1:33:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,chemistry, spiritual reality,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.30,1:33:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,AA, 12 steps.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.88,1:33:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever I could find truth, I incorporated
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.88,1:33:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it, because at some point with
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.88,1:33:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,some patient, that is just what they need,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.88,1:33:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that little extra quarter
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.90,1:33:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,ounce on the scale is what tips
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.90,1:33:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.90,1:33:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, humor.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.90,1:33:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Which I think is very therapeutic.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.14,1:33:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And to see things in a humorous way,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.14,1:33:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and pretty soon the patient begins to see things
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.14,1:33:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,in a humorous way, and gives up
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.14,1:33:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking about suicide, and considers the whole
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.14,1:33:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,thing a stupid joke.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.46,1:33:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.46,1:33:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say, don't kill yourself this week, you haven't paid
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.46,1:33:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,your bill yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.35,1:33:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,First pay my bill,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.35,1:33:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,then kill yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.35,1:33:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you son of a bitch, you'd say, walk out the
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.35,1:33:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,door, but I know he's not going to commit suicide
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.35,1:33:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.31,1:34:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I would have gotten to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.18,1:34:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's because the
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.18,1:34:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,timing of the remark was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.18,1:34:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking it out of context.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.18,1:34:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking it out of context.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.18,1:34:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it generally
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.18,1:34:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,likely that loved ones in our
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.18,1:34:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,lives, parents, children,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.18,1:34:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,siblings, are people
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.18,1:34:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that we have had relationships with
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.18,1:34:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,or known in prior lives?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.46,1:34:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask the question. We can ask
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.46,1:34:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it in a general way.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.46,1:34:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a good likelihood,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.46,1:34:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,not a determination,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.46,1:34:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,not a one-to-one, but
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.77,1:34:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,many people have been in and out of each other's lives
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.77,1:34:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,for a long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.57,1:34:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say how long.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.89,1:34:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.89,1:34:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of times.
